ğŸ’¡ Use Case: Modified Data Analysis
Imagine tracking customer record changes in Power BI using a date slicer. Simply link the ModifiedDate field from your database and filter updates after December 29, 2000â€”just like in SQL!

ğŸ”¹ SQL Query for Power BI Data Source:

